{"tid":1052562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大圍車房命案】三人獲釋　良心老闆唔請人等伙記回來：公義決定","createTime":"2019-03-08T11:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T11:31:31.000Z","uid":15229,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d04cfd16bc65f3a016bfdaa4bb5ed46192f9bf35","tid":1052562,"uid":15229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"29歲的鄭智斌，當時在鄰舖車房工作，聽到追逐聲協助制服疑人。鄭智斌惹官非後，他僱主Tim一直有作出支援。這幾個月來，老闆Tim堅持不請新員工代替鄭，要等他獲釋回來。失去自由，鄭智斌還擔心車房人手不夠，叫老闆快快請人取代自己，好老闆不離不棄，拒絕請人，工作太多，他自己落手落腳補位，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一路都留咗位俾佢（鄭智斌）」，等待鄭隨時返車房開工</span></strong>。Tim認為，控方撤控是公義的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個老闆好好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0d213ce51697fd67b41587d730ea75b972b31a","tid":1052562,"uid":15229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/303715/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E8%BB%8A%E6%88%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B-%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E5%94%94%E8%AB%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%AD%89%E4%BC%99%E8%A8%98%E5%9B%9E%E4%BE%86-%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F303715%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B-%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AB%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25BC%2599%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%259B%259E%25E4%25BE%2586-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3D